---
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Xiaomi Humanoid - Xi Lin</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white text-gray-900">
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 sm:px-10">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900">Back to home</a>
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Humanoid Motion Retargeting and Low-Level Skill Simulation</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
        At Xiaomi Robotics, I worked on humanoid motion retargeting, simulation-system construction, and low-level skill training for assembly-style and physically grounded robot behaviors.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <img src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-retargeting.png" alt="Xiaomi retargeting result" class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 object-cover" />
        <section class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Main Contributions</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            Converted human assembly videos into SMPL trajectories, retargeted motion to humanoids, built simulation environments, and benchmarked RL pipelines for dexterous and payload-related tasks.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
